ActControlled Drugs and Substances Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedules l and Vl to the Controlled Drugs and Substances Act (U-47700)
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULES I AND VI TO THE CONTROLLED DRUGS AND SUBSTANCES ACT (U-47700) in order to add a new entry to Schedule I to the Controlled Drugs and Substances Act for U-47700 and its salts, derivatives, isomers and analogues, and the salts of its derivatives, isomers and analogues. In the interest of clarity, five analogues of U-47700 (bromadoline, U-47109, U-48520, U-50211 and U-77891) are being specifically listed under the entry for U-47700.
